zornmesh tail
Live-tail envelope flow by subject pattern.

Usage: zornmesh tail <SUBJECT_PATTERN> [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --evidence <PATH>  Read this evidence log
      --output <FORMAT>  Select human, json, or ndjson output
  -h, --help  Print help

Pattern syntax follows the daemon subscription contract:
  *   matches a single subject level
  >   matches one or more trailing subject levels (last position only)

Output modes:
  human  Readable one-event-per-line summaries on stdout.
  json   NDJSON event stream with one structured event per line.
  ndjson Identical to json mode for tail.
